lead_paragraph: Juergen Klopp is eager not to let Liverpool's trophy-laden past burden his squad with the manger instead urging his players to write their own chapters in the Merseyside club's history books.

headline.print_headline: Klopp Implores His Liverpool Squad to Create Own History
